  "Description": {
    "English": "The howling of an advanced intelligence banished to oblivion, a reverberation in sentience and crystal. <br><br>Each memory in this <span class=\"name name-technology\">data packet</span> is an entire reality in itself, bearing the fingerprint of countless lives. The <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Atlas</span> will recognise this seed.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "被放逐至堙灭之中的高等智慧的尖叫，蕴藏在智慧生命与水晶之中的回响。<br><br>这个<span class=\"name name-technology\">数据包</span>中的每段回忆都是完整的现实，里面承载着无数生命的痕迹。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">阿特拉斯</span>将辨识这枚种子。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "某種已蕩然無存的高級智慧生物，其怒吼聲在智慧生物和晶體中迴盪。<br><br>這個<span class=\"name name-technology\">資料包</span>中的每個記憶本身就是一個完整的現實，承載著無數生命的痕跡。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">寰宇</span>認得這個種子。"
  },
